snippet.title: Sleep Paralysis: The Uncanny Valley Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/19...
Sleep Paralysis: The Uncanny Valley is a story-driven first-person psychological horror game. You are in a lonely house, suffering from sleep paralysis. Trying to find a cure, deal with Thomas’ worst fears and make decisions that will determine whether he is going to lose his mind or not.

Available in December.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/limitedinsi...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LimitedInStudio/
Official website: http://www.visagethegame.com

#sleepparalysis #uncannyvalley #horrorgames #horrorgaming #storygames #demon
